data.description: Dream Home with an assumable loan! Currently operating as an Airbnb, this charming pool home in Poinsettia Heights brought in over $115,000 in revenue over the last 12 months. Located just minutes from the beach, the home offers an open floorplan bathed in natural light. Upgraded throughout from floors to doors! Granite kitchen countertop, gas range & stainless steel appliances. Remodeled bathrooms. Large deck with BBQ area, tiki hut & oversized pool with brand new pool heater. Impact windows and French doors. Newish roof. All new grass. Close to the trendy shops & restaurants of the Las Olas area and downtown art scene. Well-appointed, ideally situated, this income-producing property is priced to sell. See it today!
